headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Travelers’s Q2 Earnings Call
summary: Travelers delivered a quarter that met Wall Street’s revenue expectations and significantly exceeded profit forecasts, as highlighted by a positive 5.5% market reaction. Management attributed the strong results to disciplined underwriting, lower catastrophe losses compared to plan, and robust investment income.
